OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775661069
OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,FThe BBC breached its editorial
OL,7,Fstandards when it broadcast a racial
OL,8,Fslur during its coverage of the 2026
OL,9,FBafta Film Awards, an investigation
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FThe corporation said it received a
OL,13,Flarge number of complaints after
OL,14,Fdisability campaigner John Davidson
OL,15,FMBE, who has Tourette's syndrome,
OL,16,Fcould be heard shouting a racial slur
OL,17,Fat Sinners actors Delroy Lindo and
OL,18,FMichael B Jordan as they presented an
OL,19,Faward at the February 11 ceremony.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
