FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775661069
OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,FAn investigation by the BBC's
OL,7,Fexecutive complaints unit (ECU) found
OL,8,Fthe inclusion of the slur was "highly
OL,9,Foffensive" and "had no editorial
OL,10,Fjustification", but it added that
OL,11,Fbroadcasting it was unintentional.
OL,13,FIt went on to say the slur should have
OL,14,Fbeen edited out of the version of
OL,15,Fcoverage available on iPlayer when the
OL,16,Fevent finished, but said a delay of
OL,17,Fseveral hours was caused by "a lack of
OL,18,Fclarity among the team as to whether
OL,19,Fthe N-word was audible on the
OL,20,Frecording".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775661069
OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,FThe ECU added the delay was "a serious
OL,7,Fmistake, because there could be no
OL,8,Fcertainty that the word would be
OL,9,Finaudible to all viewers".
