CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775661069
OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,FThe report said: "The ECU accepted
OL,7,Ftheir account (that the word was
OL,8,Fbroadcast by mistake), for two
OL,9,Freasons. Firstly, the use of the N-
OL,10,Fword in that instance was extremely
OL,11,Findistinct, to the point where it
OL,12,Fmight well not have been recognised by
OL,13,Fthe production team.
OL,15,F"Secondly, there was another
OL,16,Foccurrence of the N-word about 10
OL,17,Fminutes later, which was recognised by
OL,18,Fthe production team and immediately
OL,19,Fedited out in accordance with the
OL,20,Fprotocols on offensive language which
OL,21,Fwere in place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775661069
OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,F"There is no reason to conclude they
OL,7,Fwould have applied the protocols in
OL,8,Fone case while deliberately ignoring
OL,9,Fthem in the other."
OL,11,FThe report confirmed the BBC's chief
OL,12,Fcontent officer has sent letters of
OL,13,Fapology to Lindo, Jordan and Davidson.
OL,15,FCoverage went out on the BBC on a two-
OL,16,Fhour time delay, with the final
OL,17,Fprogramme edited down from the three-
OL,18,Fhour ceremony.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
