PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775661069
OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,FAt the time, then director-general Tim
OL,7,FDavie said the BBC "profoundly
OL,8,Fregrets" the incident and that it was
OL,9,F"a genuine mistake" which "should
OL,10,Fnever have been broadcast".
OL,12,FDavidson, who was at the ceremony to
OL,13,Fcelebrate a film about his life called
OL,14,FI Swear, said the BBC should have
OL,15,F"worked harder" to ensure his racial
OL,16,Fslur was not broadcast, telling US
OL,17,Fentertainment magazine Variety he "had
OL,18,Fan expectation that the BBC would
OL,19,Fphysically control the sound" at the
OL,20,Fevent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
