OL,3,CBBC breached editorial standards over
OL,4,CBafta racial slur, investigation finds
OL,6,FDuring the broadcast, the award
OL,7,Fceremony's presenter, Alan Cumming
OL,8,Fissued an apology for the language
OL,9,Fviewers may hear.
OL,11,FHe said: "You may have heard some
OL,12,Fstrong and offensive language tonight.
OL,13,FIf you have seen the film I Swear, you
OL,14,Fwill know that film is about the
OL,15,Fexperience of a person with Tourette
OL,16,Fsyndrome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
